title: Newest versions of Firefox logging me out of websites
content: Over the past few weeks, with versions 81 and 82, Firefox keeps logging me out of my 'stay logged in' websites, sometimes by just closing the browser window (with the same browser session open). I have my settings to not clear any cookie data or cache, only browsing and download history. I don't change settings routinely; this just began happening randomly. Any thoughts? Thanks--
